cdata.name: AMLT
cdata.desc:
Coinfirmis a cryptocurrencypayment platform. It provides the tools for theuser to executedigital-assets transactions through the Blockchain, on the platform.In order to assist on the transactions risk management, Coinfirmoffers the users two transaction reports for free, theOngoing Monitoring and the Standard Reports.Enterprise Reports are available for users at the platform for 12.50 USD.

The AMLT token is an Ethereum-based (ERC20) cryptocurrency developed byCoinfirm. The token can be used for prepaid services as well as to grant users the access rightsof the platform. Additionally, users can provide data and ratings on other Coinfirm market participants thought the AMLTtoken mechanism.
